FILTERING GAMES BY Genre

1. Create the state in parent component that accepts a Genre type parameter or null

2. Create the props in GenreList that accepts a function with a parameter of type Genre and pass it to the parent component

3. Pass the state from parent component to GameGrid and add it as an argument to useGames

4. Add a request config to the useGames
   .Add the parameters and arguments to useGames
   .Add the type paramater to useData of the request config
   .Add the properties from the request config to the GET method

5. Update useEffect with dependencies
   .Add the array of dependencies paramater to the useData
   .Add the dependency paramater from useData to the 2nd parameter of useEffect
   .Pass the dependency as a third parameter to the 